With this gig all packages include the following:

WooCommerce Setup

Responsive contact forms

Security and Speed optimization

After working with me youll be left with a website that is a total breeze to maintain!


Looking forward to helping you take your online presence to the next level!

questionsAndAnswers.question: what is the difference between wordpress.com and wordpress.org?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: The key difference between WordPress.com and WordPress.org is who's actually hosting your website. With WordPress.org, you host your own site (I recommend this). With WordPress.com, on the other hand, it's WordPress.com that takes care of all of this for you (easier to start, less freedom).

questionsAndAnswers.question: What do I need for a website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: You need a domain name and a hosting account, Domain name is the name of your website e.g. www.yoursitename.com and hosting is the server where all your website's data like images, text, and videos are stored.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What do you need to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
The most basic and compulsory requirements are:  
1. WordPress-friendly hosting or Linux cPanel based hosting. (If you don't have hosting yet, I can help you to decide)
2. A domain name/website name (e.g. www.yoursitename.com) linked with hosting server. 
3. Content for pages (text+images).

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide domain and hosting?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No, but I can help you decide where to host your website, just send me a message and we will discuss about it.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you start working if I don't have domain and hosting?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I can start building your website on my own hosting account and can transfer that later to your account, when you purchase your domain name and hosting.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What if i do not have the content?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No worries! I can set up the site with dummy data which you can easily edit and input your data later.

questionsAndAnswers.question: I'm not a technical person, will I be able to edit or modify my website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes! You can easily edit your website content (text+images), Update and modify with a single click, and visual drag-drop options.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What do you mean by a website with E-commerce functionality?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: By website with E-commerce functionality I mean a website with an online store. Where you can sell your products or services.

questionsAndAnswers.question: After we finish, if I require help with anything, will you help me?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, of course. If you need help with small changes, I will help you with that. I usually do not charge anything for these changes or help. However, if the change takes longer time, I might ask for a very small fee, perhaps $5-15 depending on the time required.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you use Elementor, Divi,  Beaver page builders?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No, I use Gutenberg page builder but I can use a builder of your choice and I have experience with Elementor, Divi, Beaver builder.
